OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly dry start with some
OL,6,Fbright spells. Rain spreads in from
OL,7,Fthe west through the morning,
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy. Staying drier in
OL,9,Fthe east. Brighter spells developing
OL,10,Fin the west towards evening as the
OL,11,Frain clears east. Breezy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny remaining cloud and rain
OL,14,Fsoon clearing east. Otherwise largely
OL,15,Fdry with clear spells through the
OL,16,Fnight, but the odd shower feeding in
OL,17,Ffrom the west. Occasionally blustery
OL,18,Fsouthwest winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
