OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FIt will be largely dry with
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells, though with
OL,7,Fthe chance of the odd shower. Cloudier
OL,8,Fevening with some patchy rain. A bit
OL,9,Fcooler than recent days.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FQuite
OL,12,Fcloudy Saturday morning with some
OL,13,Frain, drier and brighter later.
OL,14,FCloudy, fresh southerly winds, and
OL,15,Foccasional outbreaks of rain on Sunday
OL,16,Fand Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
